    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>You see a bald, bearded man fiddling with an old telescope, bearing signs of crude repair.

“If you want me to do a chart, you’re wasting your time,” says the man, his accent thick and heavy.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.npc_abukar_met = true;</string>
        <string>dlgTeleportToMarker(TM_PC_Abukar_01);</string>
        <string>dlgRotateToChar(1, 4920);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What chart?”</text>
          <def_link>4813</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4812</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I’m a stargazer,” says the man impatiently, as if it should have been obvious, “but I don’t do charts anymore, so don’t ask. Now, what do you want?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I need a loremaster.”</text>
          <def_link>4814</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4813</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I am that as well. Surely, you've heard about Abukar? So, tell me what you need and go away.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What is this thing?”</text>
          <def_link>4815</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I have a few items I want you to look at.”</text>
          <def_link>4823</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4814</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“A telescopium – a wonder of wonders. Through it, I observe stars and their movements, although it’s not the stars but the void between them that captures my attention now.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.npc_abukar_talkedAboutTelescope = true;</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why?”</text>
          <def_link>4816</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4815</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I’ve learned that the void is anything but empty. The darkness hides it well, but nothing can stay hidden forever. There are those who dwell in the void and I’ve taken it upon myself to watch them.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Have you seen any yet?”</text>
          <def_link>4817</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4816</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I have not, but the absences of evidence is not the evidence of absence. They are there, somewhere. I know that now.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What makes you think that?”</text>
          <def_link>4818</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4817</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“What makes me think that? The wisdom of the ancients, contained in the scrolls I found in the ruins of the library of Saross. Oh, the truth they revealed... I burned the scrolls, but I can’t burn the words imprinted in my mind. They are the reason I watch the void now.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.npc_abukar_mentionedSaross = true;</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What did the scrolls say?”</text>
          <def_link>4819</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“The library of Saross? Where is it?”</text>
          <def_link>4831</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4818</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“They said that the Magi reached far into the void and brought forth beings that are not of this or any other world, beings that know neither life, the way we know it, nor death. The link has been severed and the gates sealed, but the path remains. The seals can be unlocked and the spells can be reversed, unless we stand guard and watch the void.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.npc_abukar_talkedAboutScrolls = true;</string>
        <string>addLore(11);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Is that what the scrolls said? Word for word?”</text>
          <def_link>4821</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“You've mentioned the library of Saross. Do you know where it is?”</text>
          <def_link>4831</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear>aod.npc_abukar_talkedAboutSaross == false &amp;&amp; aod.npc_abukar_mentionedSaross</checkOnAppear>
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I have a few items I want you to look at.”</text>
          <def_link>4823</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>He’s madder than a hatter. Best leave him alone.</text>
          <def_link>4820</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4819</UID>
    </dlgPart>
