      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I’ve seen such gadgets before, but I found their design somewhat limited in application. If you keep it next to your face, you can breathe easily, even when the air is most foul, yet when you need air the most, the gadget does nothing.

“I tested it on my last apprentice – tied the gadget to his face and a weight to his legs and lowered him into a well. I pulled him out ten minutes later and he was deader than a doornail. Trust me, these trinkets are worthless, so never put your faith in them.”</npc_text>
